column4:
In this situation, I can only hope
for brave actions from Mr. Crow,
who's always hungry for food.

It's about that esteemed figure; 
without a doubt, a magnificent transformation 
will be forthcoming.

It looks like Chief Alchemist 
Diamantes is undertaking a major study; 
I wonder what will unfold.

I can sense the weakening vitality 
of the forest and the land; 
Lestania is faltering.

The gold of the Golden Country does not 
come from the land; 
it is gold born from nothingness.
